<div class="determinism-container">
    <div class="physics-examples">
        <div class="example-card">
            <h3>Newton's Laws</h3>
            <div class="formula">F = ma</div>
            <div class="animation-container">
                <div class="ball"></div>
                <div class="force-arrow"></div>
            </div>
            <p>
                Classical mechanics suggests a perfectly predictable universe where every 
                action follows inevitably from prior conditions.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="example-card">
            <h3>Conservation Laws</h3>
            <div class="formula">E = mc²</div>
            <div class="animation-container">
                <div class="energy-transformation">
                    <div class="particle"></div>
                    <div class="wave"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <p>
                The immutable laws of conservation imply a universe governed by 
                unchangeable rules and patterns.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="example-card">
            <h3>Causality</h3>
            <div class="formula">Δt > 0</div>
            <div class="animation-container">
                <div class="domino-chain">
                    <div class="domino"></div>
                    <div class="domino"></div>
                    <div class="domino"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <p>
                The principle of causality ensures that effects always follow their causes 
                in a predetermined sequence.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="implications">
        <h3>Physical Determinism</h3>
        <p>
            In a universe governed by physical laws, every event is the inevitable 
            consequence of prior events combined with the laws of nature. This raises 
            profound questions about free will and moral responsibility.
        </p>
        <div class="determinism-animation">
            <div class="universe-model">
                <div class="particle-system">
                    <div class="particle p1"></div>
                    <div class="particle p2"></div>
                    <div class="particle p3"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    .determinism-container {
        padding: 2rem;
        background: rgba(var(--accent-dark), 0.2);
        border-radius: 12px;
    }

    .physics-examples {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
        gap: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .example-card {
        padding: 1.5rem;
        background: rgba(var(--accent-dark), 0.3);
        border-radius: 8px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(var(--accent-light), 0.2);
    }

    .example-card h3 {
        color: rgb(var(--accent-light));
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .formula {
        text-align: center;
        font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        margin: 1rem 0;
        color: rgb(var(--accent-light));
    }

    .animation-container {
        height: 150px;
        margin: 1rem 0;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .ball {
        width: 20px;
        height: 20px;
        background: rgb(var(--accent-light));
        border-radius: 50%;
        position: absolute;
        left: 20%;
        top: 50%;
        animation: move 3s infinite linear;
    }

    .force-arrow {
        position: absolute;
        top: 50%;
        left: 10%;
        width: 40px;
        height: 4px;
        background: rgba(var(--accent), 0.8);
        animation: pulse 3s infinite;
    }

    .force-arrow::after {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        right: -8px;
        top: -6px;
        border-left: 10px solid rgba(var(--accent), 0.8);
        border-top: 8px solid transparent;
        border-bottom: 8px solid transparent;
    }

    .energy-transformation {
        position: relative;
        height: 100%;
    }

    .particle {
        width: 20px;
        height: 20px;
        background: rgb(var(--accent-light));
        border-radius: 50%;
        position: absolute;
        left: 50%;
        top: 50%;
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        animation: transform 4s infinite;
    }

    .wave {
        position: absolute;
        left: 0;
        top: 50%;
        width: 100%;
        height: 2px;
        background: rgba(var(--accent), 0.5);
        animation: wave 3s infinite ease-in-out;
    }

    .domino-chain {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-around;
        align-items: center;
        height: 100%;
    }

    .domino {
        width: 20px;
        height: 60px;
        background: rgb(var(--accent-light));
        animation: fall 3s infinite;
    }

    .domino:nth-child(2) {
        animation-delay: 0.5s;
    }

    .domino:nth-child(3) {
        animation-delay: 1s;
    }

    .implications {
        margin-top: 3rem;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .universe-model {
        height: 200px;
        position: relative;
        margin: 2rem 0;
        background: rgba(var(--accent-dark), 0.4);
        border-radius: 8px;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .particle-system {
        position: absolute;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
    }

    .particle-system .particle {
        position: absolute;
        width: 10px;
        height: 10px;
        background: rgb(var(--accent-light));
        border-radius: 50%;
    }

    .p1 { animation: orbit1 8s infinite linear; }
    .p2 { animation: orbit2 6s infinite linear; }
    .p3 { animation: orbit3 10s infinite linear; }

    @keyframes move {
        0% { transform: translateX(0); }
        100% { transform: translateX(300%); }
    }

    @keyframes pulse {
        0%, 100% { opacity: 0.5; }
        50% { opacity: 1; }
    }

    @keyframes transform {
        0%, 100% { 
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            border-radius: 50%;
        }
        50% { 
            width: 40px;
            height: 2px;
            border-radius: 0;
        }
    }

    @keyframes wave {
        0%, 100% { transform: scaleY(1) translateY(-50%); }
        50% { transform: scaleY(2) translateY(-50%); }
    }

    @keyframes fall {
        0% { transform: rotate(0deg); }
        50%, 100% { transform: rotate(90deg); }
    }

    @keyframes orbit1 {
        from { transform: rotate(0deg) translateX(60px) rotate(0deg); }
        to { transform: rotate(360deg) translateX(60px) rotate(-360deg); }
    }

    @keyframes orbit2 {
        from { transform: rotate(120deg) translateX(40px) rotate(-120deg); }
        to { transform: rotate(480deg) translateX(40px) rotate(-480deg); }
    }

    @keyframes orbit3 {
        from { transform: rotate(240deg) translateX(80px) rotate(-240deg); }
        to { transform: rotate(600deg) translateX(80px) rotate(-600deg); }
    }
</style>